{
  "stem": "4695.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And sometimes when they give us a place to rest overnight, they put the machine guns on high so much, even it is raining, when you stand up, you hit first-- you are short.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Then you must be like that the whole night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You don't know how long the machine guns are from shooting automatically.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Then I tell it to my friends, I plan to escape, because if I will come to the German territory, it will be very hard on the Polish territory.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I can help myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I planned-- then Polivoda, he told me-- his brother is here, I think, in Toronto-- he tell me, you know, they will kill you like a dog.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You have no chance, I think.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Listen, if they torture-- if you take two persons, a righteous man and a man who is a criminal, when you give the same torture and the criminal type could be very strong.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But he will survive-- well-- could be very weak, but he will survive, because when he is a criminal, he knows that he is-- he is not correct.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He need the punishment.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I tell them, I will not wait.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When they torture me once, the second time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then when I will be killed like [INAUDIBLE], or not this man what I was born.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I decide, I will take my luck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If I will survive, it's OK.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It not, it's nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A moment was a day we didn't water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And on the road start-- how is that-- you know how in the small towns they--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A well, and they bring water up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody, thousands, bring-- to do with-- drink water, you see?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I see I have 300 yard to go to the-- to the-- I see the trees and everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The forest.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
